dream is to go even lighter.

00:29:53.290 --> 00:29:56.720
If you're not living in
New York, or San Francisco,

00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:59.170
you're probably not walking
a lot with the board.

00:29:59.170 --> 00:30:01.450
So it's not really an
issue for most people

00:30:01.450 --> 00:30:03.310
to just throw it in
the back of their car.

00:30:03.310 --> 00:30:04.750
But we definitely
want it to be lighter.

00:30:04.750 --> 00:30:07.249
I mean, that's just probably a
better experience all around.

00:30:07.249 --> 00:30:09.730
And, you know, I do believe
that, you know, one day,

00:30:09.730 --> 00:30:11.970
you'll buy a cell phone
with all the energy

00:30:11.970 --> 00:30:13.840
I'll ever need for it.

00:30:13.840 --> 00:30:16.012
And so hopefully that
will happen at the same--

00:30:16.012 --> 00:30:16.970
with our board as well.

